name: African Cuff Fabric in Agate
description:
1 yd. of The Whimsey Chronicles African Cuff Fabric perfect for upholstery projects! All printed textiles are eco-friendly and washable. Available in 5 colorways as well as custom colors. Specify content (cotton or linen blend) and yardage needed. This listing is for 1 yard (0.91 meters) of cotton or linen blend fabric.

Pattern: African Cuff from the Jewel of the Nile Collection
Colors: Agate (shown), Jade, Lapis Lazuli, Tourmaline, Winter
Content: 8.5 oz. 100% Cotton OR 5.5 oz. Linen Blend (55% Linen & 45% Cotton)
Repeat: 18″ Horizontal, 17″ Vertical
Width: Varies depending on Content Selection – 58″ for Cotton OR 54″ for Linen Blend
Washing Instructions: Dry Clean or Machine Wash Cold using phosphate-free detergent (Dreft), Air Dry

Description: Gentle giants posture beneath sweeping arches of sparkling jewels and graceful curves of ruffles and tassels in the landscape of their ornamental jungle . . . is this how a courtship between charm and supremacy looks?

Visit my website www.whimseychronicles.com for more patterns and wallpaper options!

Digital printing utilizes a printing process that minimizes water consumption. I print on demand which means there's less waste! I suggest you order a fabric sample and view each photo attached to its listing for all product details. All items are non-refundable. Please do not hesitate to contact me with any questions.
